  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Psionic Sentry : Infinite is a anime girl action shooting  game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >use bows and various random skills to defeat enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Counterattack\" is a crucial combat tactic where bows transform into scythes to deflect enemy ranged attacks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Counterattack\" in this game isn't a highly difficult skill</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >counterattack judgment quite leniently</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >aiming for every player to enjoy the thrill of counterattacking</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Core mechanics of combat: Counterattack</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/4086fc1fbc539a60995d45d8b0ac4b70.poster.avif?t=1744900259\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/4086fc1fbc539a60995d45d8b0ac4b70.webm?t=1744900259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/4086fc1fbc539a60995d45d8b0ac4b70.mp4?t=1744900259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/6ef05fadfc7a3e05be67bfd757ff4864.poster.avif?t=1744900259\" width=666 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/6ef05fadfc7a3e05be67bfd757ff4864.webm?t=1744900259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/6ef05fadfc7a3e05be67bfd757ff4864.mp4?t=1744900259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>All \"ranged attacks\" in the game can be counterattacked</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If a series of \"long-range attacks\" are all counterattacked successfully, you will enter a \"combat close-up\" and cause a lot of damage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fighting back may seem difficult</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But I designed its judgment to be looser in order to allow any player to enjoy the fun of counterattack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Core mechanism of combat: Shield breaking</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/4430c0a58d7ea1b34f69115e6bc13776.poster.avif?t=1744900259\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/4430c0a58d7ea1b34f69115e6bc13776.webm?t=1744900259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/4430c0a58d7ea1b34f69115e6bc13776.mp4?t=1744900259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>When a shield appears on the enemy, use the corresponding skill to break the shield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroying them all will temporarily weaken the enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Core mechanism of combat: skill selection</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/3c7963ea0623ad7f3503ada85239d0c9.poster.avif?t=1744900259\" width=726 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/3c7963ea0623ad7f3503ada85239d0c9.webm?t=1744900259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/3c7963ea0623ad7f3503ada85239d0c9.mp4?t=1744900259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Players will be able to experience a variety of random skills in the game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your favorite skills to create a unique gaming experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >X：</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Psionic Sentry : Infinite is a anime girl action shooting  game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >use bows and various random skills to defeat enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Counterattack\" is a crucial combat tactic where bows transform into scythes to deflect enemy ranged attacks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Counterattack\" in this game isn't a highly difficult skill</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >counterattack judgment quite leniently</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >aiming for every player to enjoy the thrill of counterattacking</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Core mechanics of combat: Counterattack</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/4086fc1fbc539a60995d45d8b0ac4b70.poster.avif?t=1744900259\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/4086fc1fbc539a60995d45d8b0ac4b70.webm?t=1744900259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/4086fc1fbc539a60995d45d8b0ac4b70.mp4?t=1744900259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/6ef05fadfc7a3e05be67bfd757ff4864.poster.avif?t=1744900259\" width=666 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/6ef05fadfc7a3e05be67bfd757ff4864.webm?t=1744900259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/6ef05fadfc7a3e05be67bfd757ff4864.mp4?t=1744900259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>All \"ranged attacks\" in the game can be counterattacked</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If a series of \"long-range attacks\" are all counterattacked successfully, you will enter a \"combat close-up\" and cause a lot of damage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fighting back may seem difficult</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But I designed its judgment to be looser in order to allow any player to enjoy the fun of counterattack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Core mechanism of combat: Shield breaking</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/4430c0a58d7ea1b34f69115e6bc13776.poster.avif?t=1744900259\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/4430c0a58d7ea1b34f69115e6bc13776.webm?t=1744900259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/4430c0a58d7ea1b34f69115e6bc13776.mp4?t=1744900259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>When a shield appears on the enemy, use the corresponding skill to break the shield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroying them all will temporarily weaken the enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Core mechanism of combat: skill selection</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/3c7963ea0623ad7f3503ada85239d0c9.poster.avif?t=1744900259\" width=726 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/3c7963ea0623ad7f3503ada85239d0c9.webm?t=1744900259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598800/extras/3c7963ea0623ad7f3503ada85239d0c9.mp4?t=1744900259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Players will be able to experience a variety of random skills in the game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your favorite skills to create a unique gaming experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >X：</p>",
